org.ow2.proactive.resourcemanager.nodesource

Class ThreadPoolHolder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ow2.proactive.resourcemanager.nodesource.ThreadPoolHolder

  • public class ThreadPoolHolder
extends Object
    Class to hold a number of independent thread pools. Provides a synchronous access to pools allowing to submit tasks to them.
